*configuration

enable
configure

username cyberstorm password <password> level 15

interface vlan 1
no ip address
ip address 10.0.0.254 255.255.0.0

no ip http server
no ip https server
no ip ssh server
ip telnet server

bridge aging-time 60

interface range ethernet all
spanning-tree portfast

end

--

*save configuration

copy running-config startup-config

--

*show macs

show bridge address-table

*or

(echo admin; echo show bridge address-table; sleep 5; echo exit) | telnet 10.0.0.2 | awk '/:/ {print $2}'

--

*to restore factory configuration

del start
reload

